<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716293719214040687.png" title="1716293719214040687.png" alt="2b2c148030713cd176191e509210c24.png" width="718" height="308" style="width: 718px; height: 308px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">揽一怀夏日阳光，赏一幕校园风采。运动，彰显风采；奔跑，凝聚力量。跑操，作为学子们日常锻炼身体的活动，是学生体育运动的有效载体，更是展现学院风气和精神风貌的一个窗口。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">跑操进行时</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">运动先锋们迈着整齐的步伐，落地有声，踏出集体的合力与团结。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716293767460085152.png" title="1716293767460085152.png" alt="5d84a6667531e69b1ffd4dd0badd73c.png" width="719" height="456" style="width: 719px; height: 456px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">整齐的队列，铿锵的步伐，是运动先锋们演奏的青春乐章，他们脸上洋溢着青春笑容，用光芒四射的活力挥洒着青春的激情。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716293830574068242.png" title="1716293830574068242.png" alt="19325cb99fc6c8f03a8b372f4eb1828.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716293878252082450.png" title="1716293878252082450.png" alt="8dd7a4b0f08c428a42ae3480585efed.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">跑操这项体育锻炼</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">可以增强体质，提高抗病能力</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">有力地保证了学生在校学习的稳定性</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">跑操能够转移注意力</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">减轻学生学习压力，释放活力</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">还可以加强学生纪律观念</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716293910836033071.jpg" title="1716293910836033071.jpg" alt="95a920bf21f6ab0677d44cf8276bfd7e.jpg" width="705" height="445" style="width: 705px; height: 445px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 2em;">跑操</span><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">不仅仅是一项</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">平常锻炼身体的体育活动</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">更是一个育人品格品行</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">培养意志品质的集体励志活动</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716293965875058227.jpg" title="1716293965875058227.jpg" alt="75683eebe3f943a593cc92d5e2f5a7eb.jpg" width="699" height="383" style="width: 699px; height: 383px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">恰同学少年，风华正茂。在跑操中，运动先锋们用自己的实际行动诠释了青春的意义，展现出了经济管理学院学子们的朝气蓬勃、昂扬向上的精神风貌，也展现出各班级团结进取、奋发有为的卓越精神，更展现出了学校运动先锋的特色校园文化。</span></p>